nodes.text: Jedi Artisan Prestige Class is an article written by Morrie Mullins as a tie in to the Living Force campaign. It was published on the Wizards of the Coast website on April 24 2003 and introduced a new prestige class called "Jedi artisan". This was linked to Felanil Baaks who was visited the Almas Academy to train some new Jedi artisans.
